Ansible is a configuration management tool.It is a simple open-source IT Engine which automates application deployment..uses yaml scripting
Inventory: it consists of target servers/nodes private IP Addresses,usernames etc
static inventory:its static file in which we are going to list & grp our servers.the default loc of this file is /etc/ansible/hosts
dynmic inventory: it is script (python/shellscript) which fetches host details dynamattically.
playbook:set of task
ansible adhoc cmd for creating file in target server: ansible -i inventory all -m "shell" -a "touch devopsclass"
